Wednesday, October 12, 1988

MERIT DOCKET

88-1445. State, ex rel. AEI Group, Inc., v. Ohio Dept. of Commerce, Division of Securities.

In Prohibition. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Locher, Holmes, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur. Sweeney and Douglas, JJ., dissent.
